1.title: New Beginnings
1.plot: A streetwise troublemaker buys a shoddy bar in hopes of getting back on her feet. With the support of her bar manager boyfriend and long time best friend from the streets, she throws it all on the table, any means necessary, to make it a success. If her temper doesn't get the best of her, that is.
